Package minesweeper

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    Creates the JFrame holding the Tile's and populates the JFrame with the tiles as well as creates the info frame and the 2D array used by Game_Driver to control the Minesweeper game eventually passing full control to Game_Driver.
    Game_Driver
    Receives required objects from Board and takes the user input and manipulates the objects as necessary to play Minesweeper.
    Menu
    Creates the menu that the user inputs information into and then verifies input and passes the input over to Board as well as calls setIcons() to set the static icon variables in the Tile class, the entry point of Minesweeper.
    Tile
    An extension of the JButton class to be used as tiles of a Minesweeper game.
